---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";
import CTABand from "../components/CTABand.astro";

const opens = [
  "A quieting of compulsive urges",
  "A reduction in fear-driven reactivity",
  "Increased nervous system plasticity",
  "Greater access to insight and meaning",
];

const themes = [
  {
    title: "Integration as a Living Process",
    body: "Insight alone does not create change. Integration is the process of bringing what was seen, felt, and remembered into the body, the nervous system, relationships, and daily rhythms of life. It prevents spiritual bypassing and supports the reorganization of identity after profound experiences. At Casa da Nova Vida, integration is not treated as an add-on. It is central to healing.",
  },
  {
    title: "A Nervous System–Informed Approach",
    body: "Addiction and compulsive behaviors are not failures of will. They are often expressions of a nervous system shaped by threat. After ibogaine, the nervous system must learn how to live without constant vigilance. Regulation practices help establish a new baseline of safety, allowing the body to trust calm rather than seek stimulation or relief. Stability is what allows healing to last.",
  },
  {
    title: "Spiritual Integration: Remembering Who You Are",
    body: "Many who work with ibogaine report a reconnection to spirit, meaning, and inner truth. These experiences can be profound, but without grounding, they can feel distant or difficult to sustain. Spiritual integration is about embodiment, not escape. It supports living in alignment with what was revealed, rather than chasing peak experiences. Through gentle discipline, reflection, and practice, spiritual insight becomes part of everyday life.",
  },
  {
    title: "Community and Relational Healing",
    body: "Healing does not happen in isolation. Connection, when safe and attuned, helps rewire trust and restores a sense of belonging. Community offers reflection, accountability, and support during periods of vulnerability and change. At Casa da Nova Vida, we recognize relational repair as a cornerstone of lasting recovery.",
  },
  {
    title: "Structure, Routine, and Embodiment",
    body: "After profound inner change, the nervous system benefits from gentle structure. Daily rhythms, nourishing food, rest, movement, and time in nature create a container that supports consistency without rigidity. The body is not separate from healing, it is central to it. Embodiment is what turns intention into lived reality.",
  },
  {
    title: "Emotional Processing and Identity Integration",
    body: "Ibogaine can dissolve long-held identities tied to addiction, trauma, or coping. While liberating, this can also feel disorienting. Aftercare provides support as a new sense of self emerges. Emotional processing helps prevent repression, while values-based living helps rebuild identity in a grounded and authentic way. The question becomes not “Who was I?” but “Who am I becoming?”",
  },
];
---

<Layout
  title="Ibogaine Aftercare · Casa da Nova Vida"
  description="Ibogaine is a doorway, not a destination. Casa da Nova Vida offers grounded aftercare and integration so insight becomes embodied and healing becomes lived."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Ibogaine Aftercare"
    title="Integration, Regulation, and the Path Forward"
    intro="Ibogaine is not the end of the journey. It is a powerful interruption, an opening, a clearing. What follows is what determines whether that opening becomes a lasting transformation. At Casa da Nova Vida, we understand ibogaine as a doorway, not a destination. Aftercare is the process by which insight becomes embodied, safety becomes familiar, and healing becomes lived."
    image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502082553048-f009c37129b9?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80"
    imageAlt="Light breaking through a forest canopy"
  />

  <!-- Why aftercare matters -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20 lg:px-10 lg:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why Aftercare Matters</p>
      <p class="mt-6 leading-relaxed text-cocoa">
        Ibogaine can quiet compulsive loops, reduce withdrawal, and temporarily
        soften the nervous system's grip on survival-based patterns. For many, it
        offers relief, clarity, and a sense of neutrality that may not have been
        felt in years. But without integration, these changes can fade. Aftercare
        is what allows the nervous system, the psyche, and the spirit to
        reorganize around truth rather than habit. It is how insight is
        translated into daily life, and how freedom becomes sustainable.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What ibogaine opens -->
  <section class="bg-cream px-6 py-20 lg:px-10 lg:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow">What Ibogaine Opens</p>
      <p class="mt-6 leading-relaxed text-cocoa">
        Ibogaine often creates a unique window of opportunity. During this time,
        many experience:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
        {
          opens.map((o) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-cocoa">
              <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-none rounded-full bg-moss" />
              <span class="leading-relaxed">{o}</span>
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-6 leading-relaxed text-cocoa">
        This window is both sacred and temporary. Aftercare helps stabilize what
        has been opened, allowing new patterns to take root before old survival
        strategies return.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Themes of aftercare -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20 lg:px-10 lg:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
        {
          themes.map((t) => (
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-sand bg-parchment p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl text-forest">{t.title}</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-cocoa">{t.body}</p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our philosophy of aftercare -->
  <section class="bg-forest px-6 py-20 text-linen lg:px-10 lg:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow text-gold">Our Philosophy of Aftercare</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-sagelight">
        Healing is not linear. Aftercare is not time-limited. Recovery is not
        perfection. At Casa da Nova Vida, aftercare is understood as a way of
        living, one rooted in coherence, responsibility, and connection. Support
        adapts as the individual grows, honoring both the fragility and strength
        that follow deep transformation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="py-20 lg:py-28"><CTABand
    heading="Interested in Learning More?"
    body="Reach out to learn how aftercare and integration at Casa da Nova Vida can help your Ibogaine experience become a lasting new life."
  /></div>
</Layout>
